sequenceDiagram
    participant U as UserA
    participant API as SwipeService
    participant SW as SwipesStore
    participant M as MatchService
    participant N as NotificationSystem
    participant UB as UserB

    U->>API: POST /swipe {target=B, dir=right}
    API->>SW: write (A, B, right, ts)
    API->>SW: lookup reverse (B, A, ?)
    alt B previously swiped right on A
        SW-->>API: (B, A, right) found
        API->>M: createMatch(canonical_pair=min(A,B),max(A,B))
        Note over M: idempotent on canonical pair
        M-->>API: match_id
        API-->>U: {matched: true, match_id}
        M-)N: notify A {new match}
        M-)N: notify B {new match}
        N-)UB: push "It's a match!"
    else no reciprocal
        SW-->>API: not found
        API-->>U: {matched: false}
    end
